### QueryHandler Template
```csharp
using System.Threading;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using MediatR;
using Corral.Application.DTOs;
using Corral.Application.Mappers;
using Corral.Application.Queries.GetFenceById;
using Corral.Domain.Aggregates;
using Corral.Infrastructure.UnitOfWork;

namespace Corral.Application.Queries.GetFenceById;

/// <summary>
/// Handler for GetFenceByIdQuery.
/// Retrieves a single fence by identifier.
/// </summary>
public class GetFenceByIdQueryHandler : IRequestHandler<GetFenceByIdQuery, FenceDto?>
{
    private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
    private readonly FenceDomainToDtoMapper _mapper;

    public GetFenceByIdQueryHandler(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork)
    {
        _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
        _mapper = new FenceDomainToDtoMapper();
    }

    public async Task<FenceDto?> Handle(GetFenceByIdQuery request, CancellationToken cancellationToken)
    {
        var fenceId = FenceId.Create(request.FenceId);
        var fence = await _unitOfWork.Fences.GetByIdAsync(fenceId, cancellationToken);

        return fence == null ? null : _mapper.Map(fence);
    }
}
```

## Naming Conventions

| Item | Pattern | Example |
|------|---------|---------|
| Command | `[Action][Entity]Command` | `CreateFenceCommand` |
| CommandHandler | `[Action][Entity]CommandHandler` | `CreateFenceCommandHandler` |
| CommandValidator | `[Action][Entity]CommandValidator` | `CreateFenceCommandValidator` |
| Query | `[Get/List][Entity][Criteria]Query` | `GetFenceByIdQuery`, `GetAllFencesQuery` |
| QueryHandler | `[Get/List][Entity][Criteria]QueryHandler` | `GetFenceByIdQueryHandler` |
| DTO | `[Entity]Dto` | `FenceDto` |
| Entity (EF) | `[Entity]Entity` | `FenceEntity` |
| Mapper | `[Source]To[Destination]Mapper` | `FenceEntityToDomainMapper` |
| Repository | `[Entity]Repository` | `FenceRepository` |
| Service | `I[Service]Service` (interface) | `IFenceApplicationService` |

## Documentation Requirements

ALL public types and members MUST have MSDN-style XML docs:

```csharp
/// <summary>
/// One-line description (max 100 chars).
/// </summary>
/// <remarks>
/// Optional: Detailed context, business rules, edge cases.
/// </remarks>
/// <param name="name">Parameter description</param>
/// <returns>Return value description</returns>
/// <exception cref="ExceptionType">When thrown and why</exception>
/// <example>
/// <code>
/// var result = MyMethod("value");
/// </code>
/// </example>
public void MyMethod(string name) { }
```

