- ❌ Create nested classes/types
- ❌ Use anonymous or local types
- ❌ Mix multiple classes in one file
- ❌ Expose Domain entities to upper layers
- ❌ Put business logic in handlers
- ❌ Have circular dependencies
- ❌ Skip XML documentation
- ❌ Use AutoMapper or reflection-based mapping
- ❌ Have reverse layer dependencies
