## Version Control

Commit message format: `<type>(<scope>): <subject>`

Types: feat, fix, refactor, test, docs, style, chore
Scope: domain, application, infrastructure, presentation
Subject: imperative, present tense, no period

Example:
```
feat(application): Add CreateFenceCommand handler with validation
fix(infrastructure): Correct null DateTime mapping in FenceEntity
test(application): Add unit tests for CreateFenceCommandValidator
refactor(domain): Extract Position validation to separate method
```

